title: SNOWY FORTRESS UNDER SIEGE - Medieval Kingdom Total War 1212 AD Gameplay
description:
Medieval Kingdom Total War 1212 AD Gameplay - It's winter time, but that doesn't stop war.  The kingdom of France and the Duchy of Burgundy are attacking a fortress covered in snow!  The stronghold is defended by Kievan Rus and the Duchy of Lithuania.  Enjoy the Battle :D
